-- Russia May Invest Pension Cash in Stocks, Company Debt, RIA Says
-- B y   A n a t o l y   T e m k i n
-- 2012-08-03T16:32:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-03/russia-may-invest-pension-cash-in-stocks-company-debt-ria-says.html
Russia may begin investing state
pension funds in the shares of companies with high credit
ratings and local corporate debt, RIA Novosti reported, citing
legislation proposed by the  Finance Ministry .  To contact the reporter on this story:
